Ready to get started with Wondr Health? Clink the link below to register.

AT A GLANCE

Wondr Health is an informative behavior-based weight management program

  • Videos and online learning tools to educate you on how to lose weight
  • Available via desktop, laptop, or mobile device
  • Earn points for completing 10 useful lessons.

COST

Provided by your employer at no cost to you.

HOW TO GET STARTED

Register for the program on the Wondr Health website. To qualify, your BMI must be 25 or greater.
If you’re enrolled in the Wondr Health program, keep going. You will earn 750 points upon completion of lesson 10.
